name: Vorka Virus (Digital Form)
description:
Vorka Virus is an AntiMetro; Meta creatures developed by Khuzard of the Future to decimate human civilization and let earth begin anew.

Vorka comes in three forms; this initial form is a computer virus, harmless to any human physiology.

BGM by multi-instrumentalist Fabian Winandi, with suffering and death reflected by the math behind it.
"The tempo is 99, with 9 representing suffering in Japan.
It has 4 seconds of looping music. 4 is the number of death.
In 99 tempo, 4 becomes 3 bars. Vorka has a total of three forms, so 3 bars x 3 forms: back to 9 (suffering)"

Collect this OBJKT and have a chance to get the final form for free.
